text: Alexandrina Ciocan (née Vutcariova; born 7 January 1995) is a Moldovan footballer who plays as a forward. She has been a member of the Moldova women's national team. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Moldovan women's footballers Category:Moldova women's international footballers
